sequenceDiagram
    participant Buyer as Buyer
    participant BF as Buyer Frontend
    participant Backend as Backend
    participant DB as Database
    participant Admin as Admin
    participant AF as Admin Frontend

    Buyer->>BF: Click "Report Listing"
    BF->>BF: Show report form
    Buyer->>BF: Submit report with reason
    BF->>Backend: POST /reports
    Backend->>Backend: Validate input
    Backend->>DB: Create report record
    DB-->>Backend: Report created
    Backend-->>BF: Report submitted
    
    Admin->>AF: Open admin dashboard
    AF->>Backend: GET /admin/dashboard
    Backend->>DB: Get statistics and pending reports
    DB-->>AF: Dashboard data
    AF-->>Admin: Show 5 pending reports
    
    Admin->>AF: Click on report
    AF->>Backend: GET /reports/{id}
    Backend->>DB: Get report details
    DB-->>AF: Report details + listing
    AF-->>Admin: Show report details
    
    Admin->>AF: Choose action: "Remove listing"
    AF->>Backend: PATCH /reports/{id}/resolve
    Backend->>DB: Update report status and listing
    DB-->>Backend: Changes saved
    Backend-->>AF: Report resolved
    AF-->>Admin: Show confirmation